GET http://localhost:8080/applications/company/shortlist
Authorization: {{companyToken}}


### JOB SPECIFIC SHORTLIST
GET http://localhost:8080/applications/company/shortlist/6?limit=3&minScore=50
Authorization: {{companyToken}}

### SHORTLIST AN APPLICATION
